{"tid":1489540,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一瞓醒就收到和理非家姐嘅長文。","createTime":"2019-08-20T01:52:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T02:32:01.000Z","uid":175340,"like":29,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"dba51390d5ef4d65e5bc27742a60fe01a7c964c0","tid":1489540,"uid":175340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:52:38.000Z","msg":"一瞓醒就收到和理非家姐嘅長文。<br />\n<br />\n講返少少背景先，<br />\n老豆：淺藍 -&gt; 淺黃 -&gt; (71後割蓆)中立撚 -&gt; 黃<br />\n家姐：港豬 -&gt; 淺黃 -&gt; (71後割蓆)淺藍 -&gt; 黃<br />\n呀妹：核彈都唔割嘅發夢撚<br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「妹，我好想將呢段說話同個啲「文塞」嘅人講，<br />\n你估佢哋睇得明嗎？<br />\n<br />\n其實我想講一個關於我自己嘅故事，<br />\n我今年已經30歲。<br />\n30歲數仲係好後生？我唔認為。<br />\n30歲已經到中年？我未到。<br />\n<br />\n我17歲開始出嚟打工，<br />\n你話我經歷13年有成功、有成就咩？我無。<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">而且我仲係一隻「港豬」，<br />\n淨係識返工賺錢，收工返屋企訓覺。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>6月9日～100萬人上街</strong><br />\n我仲記得當日我係日本，<br />\n我朋友同我講香港嘅事，<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">我仲覺得唔關自己事添。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>6.12～放催淚彈？？</strong><br />\n我先開始感覺到呢件係一件「大事」，<br />\n我開始睇新聞，開始了解反送中。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>6.16～200萬人上街</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">我見證到香港人嘅團結，</span><br />\n同時我亦見到我份糧少左1/3，<br />\n因為生意少左=收入少左，<br />\n但我唔會埋怨係因為呢場運動令我收入少左，<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為我慶幸今天我至少仲可以用錢去換取自由。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>7.1～勇武派誕生</strong><br />\n衝擊立法會，我感覺晴天霹靂，<br />\n因為我認為曾經值得驕傲嘅和平理性抗爭消失咗，<br />\n我開始覺得我嘅經濟損失唔值得，我好唔開心。<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">然後未來20日，警察放催淚彈、拘捕、扣留，<br />\n我都覺得警察都係打份工啫，<br />\n上頭有命令，就要做架啦，無辦法架喎。</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>7.21～元朗事件</strong><br />\n直到呢日，我睇到嘅係：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">警察掉頭走，<br />\n警察唔到場，<br />\n警察話睇唔到有武器，<br />\n警察選擇性拘捕，<br />\n警察選擇性執法，</span></span><br />\n代表咗啲咩？代表咗警察係有權選擇架！！ <br />\n警察可以選擇催淚彈方向，<br />\n警察可以選擇催淚彈數量，<br />\n警察開選擇邊度放催淚彈，<br />\n警察可以選擇向邊度開槍，<br />\n警察可以選擇槍射身體邊個部位！！<br />\n所以警察不止是收order做事，<br />\n而係收左order仍然可以選擇點做！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>8.5～全民罷工</strong><br />\n我比平時早了一個鐘搭車返工，<br />\n但我感覺良好嘅係「和理非」回歸了，<br />\n我地又可以用驕人方法抗爭了。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>8.11～布袋彈射眼</strong><br />\n我第日睇直播，警察話不能證實係咪布袋彈射眼，<br />\n警察話無人報案，難查明真相，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">ridiculous!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>8.18～大遊行</strong><br />\n我同我64歲嘅爸爸+妹妹，<br />\n用左5個幾鐘去維園集會，再搵路走。<br />\n的確係人多到條路行唔到，<br />\n要行到中環先可以順利搭車返屋企。<br />\n係呢段路入面，全程落雨，時大時小。<br />\n我64歲嘅爸爸要攞住傘爬過路障，行到腰痛，腳又痛。<br />\n頭上個啲我都唔知係雨定汗，望住佢嘅背影，<br />\n我感覺佢追悔年少時沒有抗爭過，<br />\n所以即使今日開始老了，<br />\n骨頭唔聽話，都要企出黎，<br />\n陪我地行呢段路。我好感動⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">直到今日，其實我人工已經得返一半，<br />\n但我都想企出黎，<br />\n因為係麵包同自由之中，我選擇自由。</span>」<br />\n<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我想講，<br />\n一開始做革命教育家真係好攰，好辛苦。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但如果你仲重視嗰個人，<br />\n千祈唔好放棄！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n不論佢身份係家人／朋友／愛人，<br />\n不論佢係和理非／勇武，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">都千祈唔好放棄！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">終有日你會啟發到佢，相擁而泣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後不分和勇，齊上齊落！<br />\n<br />\n#香港加油 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"c00e3466880b1fb065c7b964466ad6da04699d29","tid":1489540,"uid":175340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:53:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">不分和勇，齊上齊落！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb72118e3d9488997c1615bd233389cff84e7a8","tid":1489540,"uid":175340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:54:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好放棄</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5c46465dd7b05871005f17e0093e22f0da0ef01","tid":1489540,"uid":175340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:55:34.000Z","msg":"#香港加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f332b145997038e1f9965c630c6f3b0a8d315c9","tid":1489540,"uid":175340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:55:52.000Z","msg":"721 811<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08b4bcdeb47778787da23ad5ed28300bdbccd1c7","tid":1489540,"uid":21113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:56:40.000Z","msg":"睇完決定繼續文宣聲稱中立嘅父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a145cc4e1bf5e6c3ef6f8dc84c13b7d8ae2a371e","tid":1489540,"uid":58883,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:56:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OcNkrtx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOcNkrtx.jpg&h=7b4b7984&s={SIZE}\" /> 罷買吧和理非"},{"pid":"f69a89e86355e42c40006feecd58ad2133eca17c","tid":1489540,"uid":263252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:57:15.000Z","msg":"對唔住阻個位<br />\n大陸人都夠膽玩命<br />\n你地唔通唔幫手？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該各位巴打幫手推比多d人睇<br />\n<br />\n有大陸人繼續玩命支持香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1489211\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1489211</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e8a26764a21cc10d76633d9d707f25bea1c80c0d","tid":1489540,"uid":266203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:59:52.000Z","msg":"borrow room<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">在香港長大，我們都是自己人。<br />\n勇武是和理非不可分割的一部分。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0Sc1Jd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0Sc1Jd.jpg&h=3f58bddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKyvOof.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKyvOof.jpg&h=521fe325&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3a098aa1b2a345e07620473fd292aebb96392f4e","tid":1489540,"uid":175340,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"08b4bcdeb47778787da23ad5ed28300bdbccd1c7","tid":1489540,"uid":21113,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:56:40.000Z","msg":"睇完決定繼續文宣聲稱中立嘅父母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:15:11.000Z","msg":"唔好放棄呀手足！中立撚要講道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ff4ad9ae50189f3e2fe9f81ecc314c8e13885bc","tid":1489540,"uid":175340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e8a26764a21cc10d76633d9d707f25bea1c80c0d","tid":1489540,"uid":266203,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T01:59:52.000Z","msg":"borrow room<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">在香港長大，我們都是自己人。<br />\n勇武是和理非不可分割的一部分。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q0Sc1Jd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq0Sc1Jd.jpg&h=3f58bddf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eKyvOof.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeKyvOof.jpg&h=521fe325&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:19:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">不分和勇！<br />\n齊上齊落！</span></span>"},{"pid":"10f345521c5e2d5216c18401186fdcb1f36e4126","tid":1489540,"uid":241000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:20:21.000Z","msg":"支持 推"},{"pid":"bf9153adf9603085cf2a4c9f0ed9fd939d595b38","tid":1489540,"uid":295304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:20:44.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n麻煩俾藍、淺黃、中立睇埋今日將軍澳斬人嘅新聞<br />\n<br />\n再俾佢哋睇呢個<br />\n【Timeline懶人包】警察如何放走斬人兇徒<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1489227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1489227</a><br />\n<br />\n好嬲，點解仲仍然有人支持，仍然有人覺得班垃圾處事冇問題？"},{"pid":"ab98e521d0855dbb186365f7086187146cad0b2e","tid":1489540,"uid":250557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:21:13.000Z","msg":"立場咁撚易搖擺可以黃得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a14e7266dd2d4df5e175c2accba4409c076dfe0f","tid":1489540,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:22:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"850c91b8c312313fb6f41fc7770b3c8f264812a7","tid":1489540,"uid":175340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab98e521d0855dbb186365f7086187146cad0b2e","tid":1489540,"uid":250557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:21:13.000Z","msg":"立場咁撚易搖擺可以黃得去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T02:32:01.000Z","msg":"佢再動搖我會再教育<br />\n最緊要可以齊上齊落<br />\n唔放棄！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}